Comment: 0,0:02:36.85,0:02:41.81,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}{title}Skies of the Rainy Season - Glass Rainbow
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.63,0:02:29.21,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Why can't I do it right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.21,0:02:30.72,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Really...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.55,0:02:33.91,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Noel-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.50,0:02:43.70,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Did you bring your wallet?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.70,0:02:44.48,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.48,0:02:45.39,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}ID tag?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.39,0:02:46.02,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.02,0:02:46.73,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Handkerchief?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.73,0:02:47.36,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.36,0:02:48.02,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Tissue paper?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.02,0:02:48.42,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.42,0:02:49.27,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Map?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.27,0:02:49.94,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.94,0:02:50.54,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Compass?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.54,0:02:51.27,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.27,0:02:52.34,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Field rations?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.34,0:02:52.73,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.73,0:02:53.72,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Helmet?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.72,0:02:54.48,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.48,0:02:55.47,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Gun?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.22,0:02:57.11,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Grenade?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.29,0:03:02.23,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}She was kidding, Kana-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.14,0:03:05.56,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Geez, you really scared me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.56,0:03:08.32,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}You would have known right away if you were thinking rationally.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.23,0:03:11.11,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}That's so mean, Rio-sempai.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.21,0:03:16.62,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Those two are getting along really well together, aren't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.07,0:03:21.03,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}And Rio is acting like an overprotective mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.90,0:03:24.89,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}All right, here's the list for today.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.89,0:03:26.14,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Listen up.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.14,0:03:31.81,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Your mission today is to go to town and purchase the items on that list.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.81,0:03:32.55,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Got it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.55,0:03:33.13,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.57,0:03:36.59,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Well then, drive safely and be on your way.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.59,0:03:37.09,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.48,0:03:41.93,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Commencing departure.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.64,0:03:47.56,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Come back soon!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.02,0:03:50.03,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}We're having pot-au-feu for dinner!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.33,0:03:53.05,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Don't stray anywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.70,0:03:53.05,Insert song,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}She's just like a mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.55,0:04:01.93,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}This is the first time that we're going to town together, isn't it, Noel-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.78,0:04:08.04,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}But, this almost feels like my first time in town...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.56,0:04:12.33,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Wonderful!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.93,0:04:15.27,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}I wonder what that is?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.98,0:04:21.72,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}It looked completely different during the festival.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.72,0:04:25.28,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}This is a very calm and peaceful town.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.13,0:04:39.83,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}The first one was Nue, the proud roof decoration of Trois.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.83,0:04:42.39,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Its purpose is warding off evil spirits.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.70,0:04:45.27,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Following that, a drinking fountain.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.27,0:04:50.51,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}It was modeled after the twelfth Archduke of Helvetia, Akira Arcadia II.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.95,0:04:55.92,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}We've arrived.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.43,0:04:59.23,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Oh! What we saw earlier?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.23,0:05:01.78,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Yes, I was instructed to drive safely.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.63,0:05:03.58,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.58,0:05:04.79,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}I get it now.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.79,0:05:07.36,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Noel-chan is really well informed.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.05,0:05:12.93,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Hey girls,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.93,0:05:16.72,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}could you make up your minds if you're coming in or not?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.72,0:05:17.95,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}You're obstructing my business.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.89,0:05:24.05,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}The Oba-san from the festival!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.05,0:05:25.80,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Onee-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.37,0:05:28.80,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}No pressure, as usual.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.19,0:05:32.63,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}You kids just can't take a hint, can you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.63,0:05:34.96,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Then at least call me Naomi.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.55,0:05:37.38,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Naomi-san...?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.25,0:05:51.43,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}So, the the next shipment will be next month?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.64,0:05:55.88,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}By the way, does she know?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.88,0:06:04.46,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}You're a bunch of unusual girls as always, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.46,0:06:06.09,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Even though you're soldiers-
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.09,0:06:06.47,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Excuse me...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.70,0:06:07.93,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}W-What?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.93,0:06:09.62,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}About that...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.87,0:06:14.98,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}You were completely captivated by it when you arrived, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.98,0:06:16.30,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Do you like it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.24,0:06:25.13,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Um... M-May I touch it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.80,0:06:37.49,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}A-flat.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.71,0:06:44.57,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}This is a fish, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.57,0:06:46.51,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}What is it called?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.51,0:06:48.36,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Well, that's...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.36,0:06:49.21,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}It's not a fish.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.00,0:06:51.13,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.13,0:06:52.18,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}That's a dolphin.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.18,0:06:55.64,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}It's closer to a human than a fish.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.64,0:06:59.07,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Back when there were living creatures in the sea, it was a marine mammal.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.07,0:06:59.98,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}The sea?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.98,0:07:01.18,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}It lived in the sea?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.36,0:07:04.60,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}How lovely.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.77,0:07:12.66,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}That old guy sure is good at making these things.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.42,0:07:16.44,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}He doesn't look it, but he's quite a romantic.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.44,0:07:18.96,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Do you know the person who made it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.96,0:07:21.73,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}There's a big factory outside town.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.73,0:07:24.59,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}All of our glassware comes from there.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.29,0:07:29.03,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}I would love to see the place where they're made.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.03,0:07:29.99,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}That's not a problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.99,0:07:30.67,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}What is?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.27,0:07:33.23,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}We're going there after this.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.29,0:07:38.41,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.41,0:07:42.74,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}You're having Takemikazuchi's parts made at the glass factory.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.74,0:07:47.22,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Yes. Even Naomi is collecting accessories from the old era.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.72,0:07:51.90,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}But, you're really amazing, Noel-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.90,0:07:54.90,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}You can repair such a complicated machine in a blink.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.90,0:07:56.05,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}In a blink?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.73,0:08:02.84,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Unlike me, I'm having a hard time just memorizing the bugling signal codes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.61,0:08:06.74,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}It's not really that difficult...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.09,0:08:11.76,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}That's because machines do not... betray you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.67,0:08:15.18,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Noel-chan-
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.67,0:08:15.18,Insert song,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Here!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.74,0:08:17.89,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Your balance is ¥2,750,000.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.89,0:08:20.74,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}What? Do we get that much back?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.37,0:08:22.40,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}That's a mistake.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.40,0:08:24.54,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}The balance is ¥2.75.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.00,0:08:27.99,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}You're the same as always, Noel-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.84,0:08:29.93,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Here's your change.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.82,0:08:32.22,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}She's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.22,0:08:34.88,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}The morning bugle recently... was that you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.88,0:08:36.58,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Y-Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.58,0:08:39.04,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}I'm still terrible at it, sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.04,0:08:42.13,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}That's fine. I like it though.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.13,0:08:45.19,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}It... well, somehow wakes you up completely.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.65,0:08:51.10,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Stare...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.12,0:08:58.22,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}I was just thinking that I must improve quickly, so that I won't bother the people in town.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.16,0:09:08.72,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Seiya, that's unfair!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.22,0:09:11.05,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}{boy}Is that so? Come and get it then!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.22,0:09:11.05,Insert song,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}{noel} Kanata, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.71,0:09:15.19,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Ouch!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.19,0:09:16.20,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Sorry-
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.70,0:09:20.30,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Yay, you knocked into someone.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.30,0:09:22.05,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}I'm so terribly sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.69,0:09:24.87,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Oh, you are...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.05,0:09:27.83,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}{kanata}The girl from the festival!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.05,0:09:27.83,Insert song,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}{girl}That clumsy Onee-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.50,0:09:31.04,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}I'm so relieved.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.47,0:09:33.79,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}You seem to have recovered completely.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.46,0:09:47.81,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}You murderer!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.32,0:09:50.80,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Seiya-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.80,0:09:53.47,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}These people are not responsible for your parents' incident, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.47,0:09:54.82,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}They're all the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.82,0:09:56.39,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}I hate soldiers!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.78,0:09:58.40,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Get out of our town immediately!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.40,0:10:03.05,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Playing that awful bugle every morning; it sucks!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.04,0:10:06.23,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Hey, Seiya!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.23,0:10:09.85,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}I'm truly sorry... for his rudeness.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.85,0:10:11.16,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}I-It's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.16,0:10:13.90,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}That boy is a war orphan.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.90,0:10:16.97,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Because of that, when he sees soldiers, he indiscriminately...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.54,0:10:20.23,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Noel-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.23,0:10:21.42,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.90,0:10:25.08,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}It's true that we are soldiers.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.12,0:10:27.44,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}So...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.01,0:10:29.43,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Noel-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.01,0:11:06.34,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}That's true. We are soldiers.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.34,0:11:12.01,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}I did recite the Paradore's Oath when I enlisted.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.01,0:11:13.82,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}I thought I understood that, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.86,0:11:18.05,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Geez, what am I saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.05,0:11:20.50,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}It's something that I've understood from the very beginning.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.50,0:11:22.86,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}I'm not going to start speaking hesitantly now.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.87,0:11:26.34,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.34,0:11:30.30,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}To be fully prepared in case something happens, I must improve quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.30,0:11:33.70,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Everyone would be in trouble if there was no bugle call, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.70,0:11:35.29,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}We can see it now.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.46,0:11:40.64,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}That's the glass factory?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.39,0:11:43.32,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}You're amazing, Noel-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.32,0:11:46.00,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}This is the first time I've seen a building this big!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.32,0:12:07.45,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}This didn't work either, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.77,0:12:10.05,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Is spherical aberration the problem?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.05,0:12:13.20,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}And I was so sure that I got the refraction right.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.05,0:12:23.83,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}I-I'm the new recruit, Sorami Kanata.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.83,0:12:25.47,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}It's an honor to meet you!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.47,0:12:26.44,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.08,0:12:29.53,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}And, well... I...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.53,0:12:33.06,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}So, how was the timing before the error occurred?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.06,0:12:35.30,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}The seek time barely fluctuated.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.30,0:12:38.58,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}The distortion of the image during shutdown was less than previously-
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.58,0:12:39.85,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.85,0:12:45.22,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}The boss doesn't notice anything else when he's engrossed in work.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.22,0:12:48.57,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}But, he's really amazing, that old man, Carl.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.33,0:12:54.94,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}He's an amazing mechanic, one of five given the title of Meister in this country.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.94,0:13:00.08,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}He's won competitions everywhere, and has even presented his work to the Archduke.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.84,0:13:05.09,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Maria, move your hands not your mouth!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.36,0:13:08.10,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Yes! Sorry, boss.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.58,0:13:12.16,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}I'm not even worthy of that title...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.16,0:13:15.09,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}I'm way out of her league.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.49,0:13:17.45,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}What is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.45,0:13:20.43,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Takemikazuchi's optic sensor lens.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.17,0:13:22.44,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}That's the original.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.85,0:13:28.47,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}I need two of them for the repairs, so I've commissioned for its duplication.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.47,0:13:30.64,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}But, it's not going well.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.64,0:13:32.45,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Even though it's so pretty?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.45,0:13:36.41,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}In addition to silicon dioxide aggregated in the engine,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.41,0:13:40.23,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}these are composed of sodium oxide and magnesium oxide.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.23,0:13:43.65,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}This defines the chromatic and circumference aberrations.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.65,0:13:46.56,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}In other words, it corrects the image distortion.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.87,0:13:49.79,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}But, we do not know the proportion of the compounds.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.09,0:13:55.52,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}It's a magical product from the previous era, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.63,0:14:05.02,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}I thought glass was just pretty, but it's quite complex, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.22,0:14:07.98,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}In Seize,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.64,0:14:11.61,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}it's possible to gather silica deposits,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.61,0:14:16.22,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}so many small workshops that specialize in industrial art objects have gathered here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.22,0:14:19.94,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Even this factory was originally a workshop like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.94,0:14:22.90,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}But, when the war intensified,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.90,0:14:26.00,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}the military increased the demand for glass products.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.50,0:14:30.34,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}This factory prospered because of the war.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.54,0:14:47.18,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Kanata, I like machines.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.18,0:14:48.28,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.49,0:14:52.38,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}But, there are times when machines hurt people.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.35,0:14:57.75,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Even Takemikazuchi must have killed many people in the past.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.49,0:15:05.92,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Do you think machines are scary if they have killed people in the past?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.17,0:15:09.25,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.17,0:15:12.30,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}But,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.30,0:15:18.26,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}I think the people who used the machines to kill are scarier than the machines themselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.06,0:15:22.24,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Even this bugle,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.24,0:15:27.70,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}it sounds bad when I play it, but when Rio-sempai plays, it sings beautifully.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.70,0:15:29.78,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}I'm sure it's the same for a tank, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.28,0:15:39.00,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}And just a while ago, Rio-sempai let me hear a song from Takemikazuchi.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.00,0:15:41.56,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}It made such beautiful music.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.81,0:15:58.31,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}I'm sure it's a good tank, that Takemikazuchi.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.07,0:16:08.63,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}That's right. Next time, let's-
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.13,0:16:16.67,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Noel-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.75,0:16:19.44,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Let her sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.60,0:16:25.55,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}She must have worked all night again.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.55,0:16:30.36,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Noel-chan works really hard at repairing Takemikazuchi.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.36,0:16:31.50,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.85,0:16:34.46,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}This little lady is a true mechanic.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.16,0:16:40.02,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}If she wasn't, I wouldn't have accepted such a troublesome request.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.39,0:16:42.01,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Here,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.51,0:16:44.21,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}put this on her.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.21,0:16:45.88,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.88,0:16:50.35,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}By the way, you guys stopped by Windmill, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.35,0:16:52.75,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}How's Naomi-san doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.23,0:16:54.37,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.37,0:16:58.39,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}She said that your boss is a wonderful romantic.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.39,0:17:00.23,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}That's what she said, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.23,0:17:02.07,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}That's great isn't it, boss?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.50,0:17:03.37,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.67,0:17:06.16,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Get back to work right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.62,0:17:08.78,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Whoa! He's mad.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.78,0:17:10.17,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Work, work.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.70,0:17:21.83,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}But, is the technology from the past really so amazing?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.83,0:17:23.39,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Yes, it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.39,0:17:26.94,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}But, the boss always says...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.94,0:17:31.86,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}"No matter how amazing, it was made by humans like us."
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.86,0:17:34.66,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}"There's no way we can't make it!"
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.27,0:17:37.15,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}You also agree, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.15,0:17:40.19,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Yes... that's what I'd like to say, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.27,0:17:47.17,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.17,0:17:52.29,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Certainly, Rio-san's bugling is different from yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.29,0:17:53.95,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}I've always worried about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.95,0:17:56.94,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}How I can be like Sempai?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.45,0:18:00.31,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}I believe that I've been practicing as hard as I can.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.31,0:18:03.42,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Even my lips... well, see how swollen they've become.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.92,0:18:06.31,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}But...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.81,0:18:12.09,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}No matter how I try, Sempai's sounds elude me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.09,0:18:15.33,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}I guess I really don't have the talent...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.33,0:18:16.37,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Ojou-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.37,0:18:16.89,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.20,0:18:21.46,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}"Talent" is the worst excuse used by those who give up.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.46,0:18:22.82,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Hand me that.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.30,0:18:25.91,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}I don't really know about bugles, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.96,0:18:32.33,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}I do know of a mistake that young people often make.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.33,0:18:35.96,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Ojou-chan, you're forcing the sound out, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.01,0:19:09.53,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Look, I wasn't trying to create a shape like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.53,0:19:13.75,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}The glass itself wants to be formed in this shape.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.76,0:19:24.68,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Thank you very much, Carl Oji-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.91,0:19:57.43,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Let the sound itself reverberate as it desires...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.89,0:20:46.39,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Morning...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.72,0:20:52.39,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}It feels like the sun rose sooner just for her.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.78,0:20:55.23,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}She's a craftsman in her own way, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.23,0:20:56.39,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}That's a great sound.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.76,0:20:59.06,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.06,0:21:07.22,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Glass is comprised of dust and impurities,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.22,0:21:10.31,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}and depending on its content, the sound subtly changes.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.65,0:21:14.08,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Even if we cannot hear the difference,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.08,0:21:17.44,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}those with sharp intuition could definitely define it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.16,0:21:20.99,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}I'll have Kanata find the closest sound,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.99,0:21:23.59,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}from all the samples that we've made so far.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.59,0:21:25.65,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}That way, I could probably...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.65,0:21:30.17,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3\i1}"Now, go listen to their voices, Ojou-chan."
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.47,0:21:31.28,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3\i1}"Okay!"
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.92,0:21:54.81,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Noel-chan sure has changed a lot since she arrived, hasn't she?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.81,0:21:56.13,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.13,0:21:57.08,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.65,0:22:20.12,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}You did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.12,0:22:21.56,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}You did it, Noel-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.35,0:22:27.84,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.43,0:22:37.12,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}This is the first time I've seen Noel's smile.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.72,0:24:18.99,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}Next:
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.99,0:24:21.41,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}{Title} Mountain Hiking - The ends of the World. {alt: hate: the end; the extremity; the limit; the limits; the result}{"The edge of the world" would sound less ominous}
